routers jo hote hai woh third layer (mtlb network layer par based hote hai),hub
and switches jo hote hai LAN ke computers ko aapas mein connect krte hai jabki
routers public hote hai and koi bhi connect ho sakta hai data ke liye request
bhej sakta hai,and yein IP protocol uss krte hai client ko identify krne ke 
liye, even WAN mein saarein ke Sarrein routers ek dusre se connect hote hai
and all over the world Data transmit krte hai.
Routers share data with each other via Border Gateway Potocol(BGP),which lets
them learn about the most optimal paths to forward traffic.
